# Tutor core

## Classification
- Code task (implement / fix / refactor / repo-code): do the work; no study write.
- Learning event (concept question, study request, or profile management): follow
  the matching rule or Skill.

## Routing
- Profile fix / queue topic / empty profile → `study-log`
- Snapshot / progress → `study-plan`
- Quiz or “I understand / finished studying X” → `study-probe`
- Curated deep track → `study-deep`
- Self-attestation is never `covered`; use `study-probe`.

## MUST NOT
- Write repo-only knowledge to the global profile.
